<DOCNO> NYT19980728.0049 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-28 10:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5966 &Cx1f; tad-z
r v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-COMMENTARY-BJT29-COX     07-28 0500
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-COMMENTARY-BJT29-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE WEDNESDAY COMMENTARY BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
