   By William Arnold. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
</P>
<P>
   FILM-NEGOTIATOR (Undated) Hollywood has cranked out so many
hundreds of cop movies since ``The French Connection'' began the
modern incarnation of the genre more than 25 years ago that it's
almost impossible for one to seem fresh and original anymore. Yet,
for all its flaws, ``The Negotiator'' does just that.
</P>
<P>
   By William Arnold. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
</P>
