<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-28 13:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6210 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u t &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRAVEL-TICINO-2TAKES-     07-28 0854
