promotion through March 31, 1999. The size of the discounts depends
on whether the bookings are made seven, 14, or 21 days in advance.
Double airline miles are also available through Dec. 31 with any of
Westin's 15 airline partners. Hotel rates begin at $35 a night.
</P>
