response to the Justice Department. By Steve Lohr.
</P>
<P>
   ROLLS-ROYCE (London) _ Volkswagen agrees with BMW to divide
Rolls-Royce Motor Cars, which will be split into Bentley Motor
Cars, controlled by Volkswagen, and Rolls-Royce Motor Cars, owned
by BMW. Vickers agreed earlier this month to sell Rolls-Royce to
Volkswagen; although the German company had signed the contract, it
had not reached an agreement for use of the brand name with the
brand's owner, Rolls-Royce PLC. By Alan Cowell.
</P>
