<P>
   MCCARTNEY _ LIVERPOOL, England _ Paul's yesterday is here today.
The modest government housing unit where Paul McCartney lived from
the time he was 13 until Beatlemania struck in 1964 opens Wednesday
as a protected historic site. (Roughton, Cox News Service).
</P>
