<SLUG> BC-BUSINESS-TRAVEL-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: BUSINESS AIR FARES LEVEL OFF; CLAIM FREQUENT-FLIER
MILES; DISNEY SHIP SETS SAIL 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: also moved in ``f'' category.) 
(mk) 
 By EDWIN McDOWELL   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Don't look now, but typical business air fares finally appear to
