</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-STARR (Washington) _ Former White House intern Monica
Lewinsky is granted total immunity in return for her complete
testimony in the sex-and-perjury probe targeting President Bill
Clinton, her lawyer says. By John M. Broder and Don Van Natta Jr.
(We plan to move the story by 9 p.m. ET in ``w'' news file.)
</P>
