Starr is finally hurrying, but Bill Clinton has a new, specific
reason for delay _ wanting Monica Lewinsky to testify first so he
had a chance of knowing what she says. By Jill Abramson. (Scheduled
to move by 8 p.m. ET in ``w'' news file.) 1,078 words.
</P>
